The letter from the 22.03.2024 changes the central and state share subsidy payable for the implementation of the Livestock Insurance Scheme under the Centrally Sponsored National Wine Mission. Accordingly, the following three new heads of accounts are being approved by the Government for implementation of TYE insurance scheme in the State under Scheduled Caste Application.
